items.name: Residential Time-of-Use Rg-5 (Three Phase)
items.description:
This schedule is available to all residential customers who use single or threephase
service and have measured maximum demands of 75 kW or less for at
least 8 out of 12 months and annual energy usage of 250,000 kWh or less. For
new customers, the company shall, at its discretion, determine the customer&#x;fffds
demand limits and energy usage until review of 12 month&#x;fffds service. Existing
farm and commercial customers with Measured Maximum Demands exceeding
75 kW for 8 or more of the past 12 months or whose annual energy usage
exceeds 250,000 kWh shall be immediately transferred to the appropriate rate
schedule. Customers will not be moved from one rate to another, on the basis
of conditions required to qualify for a rate schedule, more often than once a
year.
